Oliver Kaiser (https://github.com/kaiserol)

Project description:
4D Viewer is a powerful, intuitive, and extensible tool for
visualizing, analyzing, and editing four-dimensional image data.
Especially designed for microscopic and biological applications
(e.g., embryo analysis).

